family-oriented database mailer using ar_sendmail gem
Copyright (c) 2008 Kentfield School District

Uses custom email and family fields in PowerSchool to organize students
into family groups.

Includes an ldap authentication piece, tested with Mac OS X Open
Directory's ldap schema (requires ruby-net-ldap and plist gems).

Inquiries: pzingg AT kentfieldschools FULLSTOP org
 